reviewText: If you are a Mr. Bean fan then this is the case for you, it has great classics like Christmas Eve, the Department Store, and the New Years Eve one, for those of us that have a VCR still, this is recommended. Great collection. :)

The videos were as described, and the individual VHS sleeves were in good condition.  The box that held the sleeves was torn (was not included in description, did not know that I would be receiving it as well and thus hold no dissatisfaction), but the tapes were undamaged.
